{"tid":1477024,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[FB page] USD Challenge，正式啟動","createTime":"2019-08-16T04:03:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T04:26:05.000Z","uid":295548,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bb15214401a65c0eea686d376698e56186518401","tid":1477024,"uid":295548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:03:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/USD-Challenge-103297651036526/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FUSD-Challenge-103297651036526%2F&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal5zZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=2c5004d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/USD-Challenge-103297651036526/</a><br />\n<br />\n我們是一群香港人，熱血自由和民主。<br />\n<br />\n我們現正受到中國黨國體系的打壓，我們不希望在銀行的存款成為中資企業的貸款，助紂為虐；我們亦不相信港共政權並沒有透過外匯基金持有大量人民幣資產。<br />\n<br />\n對於一個連市民性命安危都無法保障的政府，我們不認為他們有能力捍衛龐大的聯繫匯率制度。<br />\n<br />\n故此，我們發起USD Challenge。<br />\n<br />\n詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n「接受挑戰者，請到銀行或找換店換取至少1000蚊美元現鈔，拍照上傳至社交媒體，同時附上此段文字並標籤三名好友，向他們發起挑戰。」<br />\n<br />\nWe are a group of Hongkongers embracing freedom and democracy.<br />\n<br />\nWe are currently oppressed by the China party state system. We don&rsquo;t want our deposits in bank becomes loans for Chinese enterprises. Such action is assisting tyrant to act brutally. Also, we don&rsquo;t believe that the communist regime in Hong Kong doesn&rsquo;t hold large portion of RMB assets through Exchange Funds. <br />\n<br />\nWe don&rsquo;t think that the Government is able to defend the huge Linked Exchange Rate System because the Government cannot even protect citizens&rsquo; lives.<br />\n<br />\nTherefore, we launch USD Challenge.<br />\n<br />\nThe flow is as followed:<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;To those who accept the challenge, please go to banks or exchange stores, get at least $1000 USD cash, take a photo and upload to any social media. At the same time, attach this paragraph, tag three friends and challenge them.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"6aa210414d